cdata.name: Urbit Data
cdata.desc:
Urbit Data is a blockchain-based platform that aims to create transparency and efficiency in the real estate market. Urbit Data has a product which offers ad-hoc evaluation of real estate object in the Spanish market. The Urbit Data's team developed a data collection engine which gathers information from various publicly available data sources and combines them in order to be able to calculate the value of real estate property in Spain. Using blockchain technology, Urbit Data intends to create an ecosystem where information on real estate properties can be digitally stored, evaluated and transferred. 

URB is an ERC20 utility token that powers the Urbit Data platform.
